data.description: Nestled on a picturesque corner lot, this charming house exudes timeless allure. Its newer roof and A/C ensure year-round peace of mind, while seamlessly blending classic charm and modern comfort. Its inviting facade welcomes you home to a world of tranquility. Inside, discover cozy spaces bathed in natural light, perfect for creating cherished memories. All this plus easy access to Atlanta-Hartsfield Airport, Camp Creek Marketplace and more.
